        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The Uttar Pradesh Social Welfare Department offers a Pre Matric Scholarship specifically designed to support Other Backward Class (OBC) students who are financially disadvantaged and pursuing secondary education in Class 9 or 10. This scholarship program recognizes the importance of education in empowering students from marginalized communities and aims to bridge the financial gap that might otherwise hinder their academic progress. By providing financial assistance, the scholarship helps alleviate the financial burden on SC families and encourages students to complete their matriculation, opening doors to further educational opportunities and brighter futures.\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n- ₹150/- per months (for max 10 months).\n- ₹750/- per annum (residential students).\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "The Uttar Pradesh Social Welfare Department offers a Pre Matric Scholarship for Other Backward Class (OBC) students. This scholarship aims to financially assist students from these categories to pursue secondary education and complete their matriculation.",
        "exclusions_md": "",
