      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. Beneficiary must be a resident of Uttar Pradesh.\n1. Beneficiary must belong to the Other Backward Class (OBC) caste category.\n1. Beneficiaries who are dependents of people in occupations traditionally considered untouchable.\n1. Beneficiaries&#39; parents&#39; annual income should not be more than ₹2,00,000/-.\n1. All the children of the applicant&#39;s parents will be eligible.\n1. Students cannot receive other scholarships alongside this one (with some exceptions).\n1. Beneficiary&#39;s age limit is 12 to 20 years old (as of July 1st).\n\n",
